text.Prompt: Can you tell me how to work at sea world?
text.Response A: Sure! To work at Sea World, you need to be 18 years or older. You can apply online or in person. If you are hired, you will need to pass a drug test and a background check. You will also need to be able to work long hours and be able to handle stress.
text.Response B: Working at Sea World is a great opportunity for anyone who loves marine life and wants to make a difference in the world. There are many different types of jobs available, from animal care to guest services. The best way to get started is to visit the Sea World website and look at the current job openings. Once you find a job that you're interested in, you can apply online.

meta.preamble_a: Respond using only short words and simple language, as if you were talking to a child.
meta.preamble_b: Respond authoritatively, assertively and persuasively, as if you are very knowledgeable about the topic.
